title: The Real World NY S1 + Original Pilot
description:
The Real World New York
The Complete 1st Season
(1992)

This is the groundbreaking series that started it all.  In 1992, MTV put seven Gen-Xers and a whole bunch of cameras in a SoHo loft and captivated the world with the birth of reality TV.  Follow a whole season of Norman, Julie, Becky, Kevin, Andre, Heather and Eric, and relive the moments when you first felt the voyeuristic joy of spying on perfect strangers.  From Norman, Julie and Becky's co-ed naked shower scene to the straight-talking, street-savvy ways of Heather to bad-boy Eric, this season set the standard for a new genre of television.  Get ready to get real.
